{"tid":1630243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）荃灣要人","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:57:25.000Z","uid":327994,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa040ee0ad5b1479d30e4bba39b89802ed136640","tid":1630243,"uid":327994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"我知今日係攰㗎啦<br />\n但我哋喺沙咀道球場等大家㗎！<br />\n8點見"},{"pid":"96e0d0aa04f271399799b32a1a533392bd4a0437","tid":1630243,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"連登要開始成熟啦！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630213</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"39860bce7de43f7de8b87cbb212ccaa56ce82e76","tid":1630243,"uid":59998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:35.000Z","msg":"P 牌仔，係都唔係今晚啦"},{"pid":"d8b3a80295ac9810d51dec772c678b14fed90b2e","tid":1630243,"uid":162287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:37.000Z","msg":"p牌仔唔好帶風向"},{"pid":"219a68bb27430103b1fe0d2b15665eb7ae591b46","tid":1630243,"uid":94151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa040ee0ad5b1479d30e4bba39b89802ed136640","tid":1630243,"uid":327994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"我知今日係攰㗎啦<br />\n但我哋喺沙咀道球場等大家㗎！<br />\n8點見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"收啦"},{"pid":"9fd3b3a0bab6ca31fcfee0e1525a5523f5c680fd","tid":1630243,"uid":320457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:56:05.000Z","msg":"就算今晚出有幾多個人黎到？<br />\n仲有好多手足係嗰邊打緊出唔到嚟"},{"pid":"49acaa27d1a343e122cb9e81c09f545cc0a197fa","tid":1630243,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:56:21.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"6d2cb2e33a34e9416ed7a1676ae35625434b9399","tid":1630243,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"不推文"},{"pid":"41d5c55c7c04ddbab0409f4f7101c853453c21dd","tid":1630243,"uid":327994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:57:25.000Z","msg":"我知有人返咗嚟，我會堅持唱歌㗎"}]}